first_appeal_template.body:
To,
The First Appellate Authority,
{department_name},
{department_address}

Sub: First Appeal against non-receipt of information under RTI Act, 2005

I, {applicant_name}, had filed an RTI application dated {rti_date} (Registration No: {ref_number}) with your office seeking information about {subject}. However, I have not received any response within the stipulated period of 30 days as required under Section 7(1) of the RTI Act, 2005.

I hereby file this First Appeal under Section 19(1) of the RTI Act, 2005, requesting that:
1. The PIO be directed to provide the requested information immediately.
2. Action be taken against the PIO for failure to respond within the stipulated time.

Date: {appeal_date}
{applicant_name}
{applicant_address}
